<section>
<div class="verse-wrapper" id="a39" onclick="ayaclick(this.parentNode,1);">
<div class="verse-number">39</div>
</div>
<div class="content-wrapper" onmouseover="this.children[0].appendChild(OQP.ayabar);">
<div class="verse-options"></div>
<div class="quran-content">يٰصىٰحِبَىِ السِّجنِ ءَأَربابٌ مُتَفَرِّقونَ خَيرٌ أَمِ اللَّهُ الوٰحِدُ القَهّارُ</div>
<div class="trans-wrapper">
<div class="trans-content-wrapper">
<h2 class="trans-content-ltr">MUHAMMAD HAMIDULLAH</h2>
<div class="trans-content-ltr">
<p>O mes deux compagnons de prison! Qui est le meilleur: des Seigneurs &eacute;parpill&eacute;s ou Allah, l'Unique, le Dominateur supr&ecirc;me?</p>
